{"tid":2007292,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登行動post已經不再奏效","createTime":"2020-05-08T09:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T17:02:20.000Z","uid":320316,"like":44,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"80e3680d5255e1736e8f6ba772edcb107f880adc","tid":2007292,"uid":320316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:08:37.000Z","msg":"連登又好 tg都好 基本上比黑警監控哂 <br />\n只要有咩post吹雞去邊 黑警就會係個果地方部署<br />\n結果被捕既就只有肯出去既手足 <br />\n而絕大多數人好大機會仲係屋企睇緊直播 係live post討論 點解出去送頭 blah blah blah<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我唔係分化撚 手足決定要出去我無權阻止 <br />\n但係你地決定出去既手足 一定要記住<br />\n今時今日已經唔再係半年前咁 無論係咩原因都好 我地必須承認 我地人數係少左極多<br />\n出到去記住<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">不被捕</span></ins></strong>一定係放第一位  <br />\n切記切記再切記 唔好再戀戰 <br />\n我地人多既時候 戀戰都令到我地咁多人比人拉 <br />\n依家我地人少 你仲想戀戰? 為左屌狗 為左對峙搞到被包圍真係值得? <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPP又好旺角又好黃大仙都好 <br />\nBE WATER MY FRIEND"},{"pid":"5b26bd4ae055107e5560752f6ab3379295115d64","tid":2007292,"uid":307619,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:09:10.000Z","msg":"【郭偉强找數】<br />\n<br />\n呼籲集體投訴社工之恥郭偉强蓄意襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n郭偉强社工註冊編號：11071<br />\n罪行：普通襲擊<br />\n<br />\n下載「社會工作者註冊局」投訴表格<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.swrb.org.hk/Documents/complaint.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.swrb.org.hk%2FDocuments%2Fcomplaint.pdf&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=c89170bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.swrb.org.hk/Documents/complaint.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"5d68377bbbac0a5a492cde19a1ddbee9e4e9fcb4","tid":2007292,"uid":320316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:10:14.000Z","msg":"求pish p牌仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5839b3b1b13103531254be1416782e366a18608f","tid":2007292,"uid":320316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T09:12:06.000Z","msg":"推阿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkg